OOC: sorry rdahl, rauq, and everyone else waiting to get chars of 
cybertron for holding you all up....

::Havotron/Dreadwind/Darkwing/Scrapper/Needlenose/Repugnus/JetV/Crotal
e/Slag::

Havotron looked to the bots around him.  "Dreadwind Darkwing, carry 
Scavenger back to the ship, it will be much faster."

The two bots combined and once again roared off grabbing at Scavenger.

Havotron spoke again over comm link..."Spinister, Needlenose... hurry 
and get the bots at the bar. WE are readying to leave."

He then jumped into the air and flew for the ship base.

Scrapper smiled. "Yes, it will be complete so we can leave now."

Repugnus still huddles in the corner could not wait to leave and rid 
this peice of tin planet.

Crotale huddled in the small weapons storage waited for the take off.

JetV spoke to Pacifix. "It is time Pacifix, the bots are on the ship 
and ready to leave. You should make your speach now and we can leave."

(hint, hint rauq)

Slag stood looking to commander Grimlock of the Dinobots.  "You are 
strong Grimlock, you should be leader, not pathetic Pacifix.
